HEADWORD: petrohyoid
<hw>pet`ro*hy"oid</hw> <pr>(p⟦ecr⟧t`r⟦osl⟧*h⟦imac⟧"oid)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Petro</ets> + <ets>hyoid</ets>.]</ety>
